task.description:
@flow(name="minivess-biostatistics") def run_biostatistics_flow(config, trigger_source="manual", **kwargs) -> BiostatisticsResult.
Task sequence: 1. task_discover_source_runs(mlruns_dir, experiment_names) 2. task_validate_source_completeness(manifest, min_folds, min_conditions) 3. task_build_biostatistics_duckdb(manifest, mlruns_dir, output_path) 4. task_compute_pairwise_comparisons(db_path, config) [parallel] 5. task_compute_variance_decomposition(db_path, config) [parallel with 4] 6. task_compute_rankings(db_path, pairwise, config) 7. task_generate_figures(db_path, pairwise, variance, rankings, output_dir) 8. task_generate_latex_tables(pairwise, variance, rankings, output_dir) 9. task_log_biostatistics_run(manifest, db_path, figures, tables, pairwise, variance)
Uses _prefect_compat.py for graceful degradation without Prefect. Fingerprint-based short-circuit: if source runs haven't changed, skip.
